</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d166n1-ptr" id="PJA13d166n1">1</a>

   <p>That is, the undisturbed tranquility of the happy mind.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d166n2-ptr" id="PJA13d166n2">2</a>

   <p>In the Letterbook copy, the remainder of this sentence is underlined.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d166n3-ptr" id="PJA13d166n3">3</a>

   <p>In the Letterbook copy, the remainder of this sentence is underlined.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d166n4-ptr" id="PJA13d166n4">4</a>

   <p>Jays letters were of <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-12-02-0205" class="document">18 March</a> and <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-12-02-0268" class="document">15 April</a> (vol. 12:334335, 410).</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d166n5-ptr" id="PJA13d166n5">5</a>

   <p>Signature in <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s hand.</p>

